title: SwiftTEA: Ana Is An Easter Egg For Enchanted?!
description:
This is the biggest SwifTEA we have done yet because a member of the 13 podcast is an actual Easter egg and was seen by Taylor Swift herself! What is even going on? And what is she trying to tell us?
Happy Red TV eve! We are honored to be joining People Magazine on Twitter to celebrate Red (Taylor’s Version). Join in on the discussion with us! You can follow along on our personal Twitter pages, @anacast31, @nickadamstweets, @laceygee.
What did we miss? What are you the most excited about coming up? Let us know!
